Name: ServiceArtifactReference
SummaryComment: Specifies the service artifact reference id used to set same image version for all virtual machines in the scale set when using 'latest' image version.

Key.Name: Id
Key.SummaryComment: The service artifact reference id of ServiceArtifactReference
Key.RemarksComment: The service artifact reference id in the form of /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroup}/providers/Microsoft.Compute/galleries/{galleryName}/serviceArtifacts/{serviceArtifactName}/vmArtifactsProfiles/{vmArtifactsProfilesName}
